SELECT COUNT(*) FROM company_name AS cn, movie_companies AS mc, title AS t WHERE t.id = mc.movie_id AND mc.company_id = cn.id AND  cn.country_code !='[pl]'  AND (cn.name LIKE '%Film%' OR  cn.name LIKE '%Warner%') AND  mc.note IS NULL AND  t.production_year >= 1950 AND  t.production_year <= 2000 ;

SELECT COUNT(*) FROM company_type AS ct, movie_companies AS mc, movie_info AS mi WHERE mc.company_type_id = ct.id AND mc.movie_id = mi.movie_id AND  ct.kind ='production companies' AND  mc.note IS NULL AND  mi.info IN ('Sweden', 'Norway', 'Germany', 'Denmark', 'Swedish', 'Denish', 'Norwegian', 'German') ;
